        <h1>京庭净水器 产品亮点</h1>

        <h2 class="section-title section-core-highlights">🌟 核心产品优势 🌟</h2>
        <div class="card-grid">
            <div class="card highlight-feature">
                <h2>1. AI动态活水：拒绝陈水</h2>
                <p class="differentiation-score stars-5">✨ <span class="stars">★★★★★</span> <span class="score-text">(行业罕见的主动“零陈水”循环)</span></p>
                <span class="tech-detail">核心卖点：</span>
                <p>不间断循环，拒绝超过3小时的陈水。</p>
                <span class="tech-detail">技术解读：</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>独创动态水循环系统，AI智能判断并主动换水。</li>
                    <li>自动排出净水箱底部陈水，注入新鲜纯水。</li>
                    <li>确保水箱内水质时刻流动新鲜，告别沉积水垢与异味。</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="patent-note"><strong>专利号：</strong> CN221720568U</p>
                <span class="tech-detail">营销思路：</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>“深夜3h未取水 → 自动换水”动画演示。</li>
                    <li>对比图强化痛点，打造爆点。</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card highlight-feature">
                <h2>2. 水质实时同屏：安心看得见</h2>
                <p class="differentiation-score stars-3">✨ <span class="stars">★★★☆☆</span> <span class="score-text">(市面双TDS显示功能占比约一成)</span></p>
                <span class="tech-detail">功能解读：</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>左侧“原水TDS”实时刷新，右侧“纯水TDS”同步显示。</li>
                    <li>净化前后水质变化一目了然，饮用更安心。</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card highlight-feature">
                <h2>3. AI智慧节水：多喝50%</h2>
                <p class="differentiation-score stars-4">✨ <span class="stars">★★★★☆</span> <span class="score-text">(动态废水比稀缺，73%净水率高段位)</span></p>
                <p><strong>能效备注：</strong> 此款为1级水效 (对比老款3级水效显著提升)</p>
                <span class="tech-detail">技术解读：</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>独创AI动态调节废水排放，高精度双TDS实时监测。</li>
                    <li>水质好少废水，水质差精准排废。</li>
                    <li>告别固定排废，延长滤芯寿命，减少换水。</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="patent-note"><strong>专利号：</strong> CN208182644U</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card highlight-feature">
                <h2>4. 大容量高水效：畅饮无忧</h2>
                <p class="differentiation-score stars-3">✨ <span class="stars">★★★☆☆</span> <span class="score-text">(大水箱与高水效组合更有说服力)</span></p>
                <p><strong>对比备注：</strong> (对比老款3级水效产品)</p>
                <span class="tech-detail">优势解读：</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>6.2L超大总容量（5L原水箱 + 1.2L纯水箱）。</li>
                    <li>AI智慧节水加持，提升单箱水可用量。</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card highlight-feature">
                <h2>5. 双重UV守护：全程洁净</h2>
                <p class="differentiation-score stars-4">✨ <span class="stars">★★★★☆</span> <span class="score-text">(多数仅单UV，双区覆盖更全面)</span></p>
                <span class="tech-detail">技术解读：</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>京庭净™双区独立UV紫外线杀菌系统：
                        <ul>
                            <li>存储水持续消毒。</li>
                            <li>出水关键路径二次把关。</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li>从“净化完成”到“即饮入口”全程无菌。</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="patent-note"><strong>专利号：</strong> CN107285542B</p>
                <span class="tech-detail">营销思路：</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>对比单UV杀菌盲区，突出航空级除菌标准。</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card highlight-feature">
                <h2>6. AI滤芯预测：精准换芯</h2>
                <p class="differentiation-score stars-3">✨ <span class="stars">★★★☆☆</span> <span class="score-text">(算法预测优于简单计时)</span></p>
                <span class="tech-detail">技术解读：</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>独创AI滤芯管理，三维数据精准预测寿命。</li>
                    <li>避免“过度更换”与“忘记更换”。</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="patent-note"><strong>专利号：</strong> CN107285542B</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-title section-filter-experience">💧 精湛过滤与便捷体验 💧</h2>
        <div class="card-grid">
            <div class="card filtration-experience">
                <h2>1. 航空级精滤：纯净甘泉</h2>
                <p class="differentiation-score stars-2">✨ <span class="stars">★★☆☆☆</span> <span class="score-text">(过滤精度达标，层数/矿化亮点不足)</span></p>
                <p><strong>营销策略：</strong> (不把“4级”单独列为核心)</p>
                <span class="tech-detail">四级精滤结构：</span>
                <ul class="filter-level">
                    <li><strong>水箱PP棉初滤：</strong>拦截大颗粒杂质。</li>
                    <li><strong>CTO前置活性炭：</strong>吸附余氯、异味。</li>
                    <li><strong>RO反渗透核心滤芯 (0.0001μm)：</strong>强力去除重金属、细菌等。(可提及RO膜品牌)</li>
                    <li><strong>CTO后置活性炭：</strong>改善口感，出水甘甜。</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card filtration-experience">
                <h2>2. 多档调温即热：3秒即享</h2>
                <p class="differentiation-score stars-1">✨ <span class="stars">★☆☆☆☆</span> <span class="score-text">(行业基本标配)</span></p>
                <span class="tech-detail">功能描述：</span>
                <ul>
                    <li>无需等待，3秒即享鲜活热水。</li>
                    <li>四档水温一键即达：常温、45℃(冲奶)、85℃(茗茶)、100℃(泡面)。</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="card filtration-experience">
                <h2>3. 便捷出水：定量解放双手</h2>
